Class HostNodePair

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.samples.simpleforwarding.HostNodePair
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class HostNodePair
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class that represent a pair of {Host, Node}, the intent of it is to be used as a key in the database kept by IPSwitching module where for every Host, Switch we will have a Forwarding Rule that will route the traffic toward the /32 destination
